OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FAnger as children left     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fstranded on train platform 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A father has criticised a train        
OL,6, operator after his two children were   
OL,7, left stranded on a railway platform.   
OL,9,FBen Newman, from Hastings, said he was 
OL,10,Fon the train when it pulled away after 
OL,11,Fhe got separated from his two boys.    
OL,13,FHe said the train doors did not re-open
OL,14,Fafter it stopped at their station in   
OL,15,FEastbourne - despite his frantic       
OL,16,Fappeals to train staff.                
OL,18,FGovia Thameslink Railway (GTR) has     
OL,19,Fapologised and said it was reviewing   
OL,20,Fthe incident.                          
